<BaseLayout
  title="3D Scanning & Drone Services in Miami, FL"
  description="Professional 3D laser scanning, Matterport virtual tours, and drone mapping in Miami and South Florida. Serving Brickell, Coral Gables, Wynwood, Miami Beach. Call (786) XXX-XXXX."
  keywords="3d scanning miami, matterport miami, drone services miami, laser scanning south florida"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">3D Scanning & Drone Services in Miami, Florida</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl mb-4">Serving Miami Since 2019</p>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mb-8">
          Professional 3D laser scanning, Matterport virtual tours, and commercial drone services throughout Miami-Dade and South Florida.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold">Get Free Miami Quote</a>
